headline: Goldman Sachs downgrades Target on slowing sales
summary: Investing.com -- Goldman Sachs downgraded Target Corp (NYSE:TGT) to "Neutral" from "Buy," given concerns about a weaker recovery in discretionary categories, increased downside risk to earnings, and signs of slowing sales.
